<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7624027>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus and inflorescence details of parental and hybrid Teucrium taxa. A. Teucrium lanigerum; B. Teucrium × murcigerum; C. Teucrium murcicum; D. Detail of Teucrium × murcigerum. All from the type locality near Calarreona, Murcia Province, Spain." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7624027/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7624029>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Flower and fruit morphology of parental and hybrid Teucrium taxa. A. Teucrium lanigerum; B. Teucrium × murcigerum; C. Teucrium murcicum; 1. Flower in lateral view; 2. Flower in dorsal view; 3. Flower in ventral view; 4. Corolla in lateral view; 5. Dissected calyx (outer side); 6. Fruits." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7624029/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

